!! Third-Party Components

`modules/hover-tilt.min.js` vendors hover-tilt's own prebuilt Web Component as-is (TiddlyWiki module header prepended, one trailing `export` statement removed — see the project's README) — no separate runtime dependency is loaded at wiki runtime. It embeds a compiled copy of the Svelte runtime internally.

